name: Account
desc:
Account information, which is exposed for information and debugging purposes
and should be ignored in most cases.

name: mimetypes
desc: Android mimetypes provided by this account.

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: type
desc: Account type, e.g. com.google or com.facebook.messenger.

name: customLabel
desc: Custom label, if label is AddressLabel.custom.

name: hashCode
desc: The hash code for this object.

name: state
desc: US state, or region/department/county on Android.

name: subLocality
desc: Anything else describing the address (iOS only).

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: includeNonVisibleOnAndroid
desc:
Non-visible contacts on Android are contacts that are not part of a group,
and are excluded by default.

name: includeNotesOnIos13AndAbove
desc: Whether to include notes in the properties on iOS13 and above.

name: returnUnifiedContacts
desc: Return unified contacts instead of raw contacts.

name: vCardVersion
desc:
The vCard version to use when exporting to VCard. V4 is the most current,
but V3 is the most commonly supported.

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: delete
desc: Deletes the contact from the database.

name: hashCode
desc: The hash code for this object.

name: id
desc: The unique identifier of the contact.

name: insert
desc: Inserts the contact into the database.

name: isStarred
desc: Whether the contact is starred (Android only).

name: isUnified
desc: Whether this is a unified contact (and not a raw contact).

name: photoFetched
desc: Whether the high-resolution photo was fetched.

name: photoOrThumbnail
desc: Returns the full-resolution photo if available, the thumbnail otherwise.

name: thumbnail
desc: A low-resolution version of the photo.

name: thumbnailFetched
desc: Whether the low-resolution thumbnail was fetched.

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: update
desc: Updates the contact in the database.

name: customLabel
desc: Custom label, if label is EmailLabel.custom.

name: hashCode
desc: The hash code for this object.

name: isPrimary
desc:
Whether this is the email address to email by default for that contact
(Android only).

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: deleteContact
desc: Deletes one contact from the database.

name: deleteGroup
desc: Deletes a group (or label on Android).

name: getGroups
desc: Fetches all groups (or labels on Android).

name: insertContact
desc: Inserts a new contact in the database and returns it.

name: insertGroup
desc: Inserts a new group (or label on Android).

name: openExternalEdit
desc: Opens external contact app to edit an existing contact.

name: openExternalInsert
desc: Opens external contact app to insert a new contact.

name: openExternalPick
desc: Opens external contact app to pick an existing contact.

name: openExternalView
desc: Opens external contact app to view an existing contact.

name: removeListener
desc: Removes a listener to contact database changes.

name: requestPermission
desc:
Requests permission to read or read/write contacts. Returns true if
granted, false in any other case. Note: read-only mode is only applicable
to Android.

name: updateContact
desc: Updates existing contact and returns it.

name: updateGroup
desc: Updates a group (or label on Android).

name: Group
desc: Group (called label on Android and group on iOS).

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: hashCode
desc: The hash code for this object.

name: prefix
desc: Prefix / title, e.g. "Dr" in American names.

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: Note
desc: Note, i.e. a free-form string about the contact.

name: hashCode
desc: The hash code for this object.

name: phoneticName
